Class BinaryNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • tech.gitpicard.jcalc.ast.Node
      • tech.gitpicard.jcalc.ast.BinaryNode
  • public final class BinaryNode
extends Node
    A node that branches with an expression on the left and an expression on the right. An operation will be applied that requires two values.
